Privacy Policy Flink Website & App
Welcome to Flink! In the following, we would like to inform you about the data we process from you when you use our services via our website or our mobile applications.
1. Controller and contact details of the data protection officer
2. Purposes and legal bases of data processing
2.1.	Automatically collected access data
2.2.	Contact us
2.3.	Registration and login
2.4.	Orders
2.5.	Product recommendations and existing customer advertising
2.6.	Sending newsletters via WhatsApp
2.7.	Applications
3. Use of cookies and similar technologies
3.1. Essential tools
3.1.1. Own cookies
3.1.2. Segment Consent Manager
3.1.3. Typeform
3.1.4. Datadog
3.2. Functional tools
